@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam dpi 180

title 图9 QA 全量门禁时序图

actor QA
participant "run_full_gate.ps1" as Gate
participant "Maven" as Mvn
participant "Vitest" as Vitest
participant "Flutter Test" as FTest

QA -> Gate : 执行一键门禁
Gate -> Mvn : mvn test
Mvn --> Gate : 回归+压测+故障注入结果
Gate -> Vitest : npm run test -- --run
Vitest --> Gate : 前端测试结果
Gate -> Vitest : npm run build
Vitest --> Gate : 构建可通过
Gate -> FTest : flutter test
FTest --> Gate : 移动端测试结果
Gate --> QA : 汇总 PASS/FAIL

@enduml